OL,3,CThree escape injury following pipe
OL,4,Cbomb attack on property
OL,6,FThree people have escaped injury after
OL,7,Fa pipe bomb attack on a property in Co
OL,8,FAntrim.
OL,10,FPolice said a pipe bomb was placed on
OL,11,Fa window ledge at Rectory Gardens in
OL,12,FBroughshane on Wednesday night.
OL,14,F"It was reported that a pipe bomb was
OL,15,Fplaced on a living room window ledge
OL,16,Fby two men dressed in dark clothing at
OL,17,Faround 11.00pm.
OL,19,F"Three people were present in the home
OL,20,Fat the time," a police spokesperson
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU|D@MO]
