OL,3,CThree escape injury following pipe
OL,4,Cbomb attack on property
OL,6,F"The device exploded and caused
OL,7,Fextensive damage to windows and the
OL,8,Fliving room of the property.
OL,10,F"Thankfully, the residents were
OL,11,Funinjured."
OL,13,FThey said the two men left the scene
OL,14,Fin a dark-coloured hatchback car,
OL,15,Fwhich made off in the direction of
OL,16,FBallymena.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@KO]
