OL,3,CThree escape injury following pipe
OL,4,Cbomb attack on property
OL,6,F"Our officers and ammunition technical
OL,7,Fofficers (ATO) attended and cordons
OL,8,Fremain in place at the scene this
OL,9,Fmorning as our inquiries continue,"
OL,10,Fthe police spokesperson said in a
OL,11,Fstatement on Thursday morning.
OL,13,F"An investigation is under way and we
OL,14,Fwould ask anyone who noticed any
OL,15,Fsuspicious activity in the area,
OL,16,Fparticularly anyone who may have CCTV,
OL,17,Fdoorbell or dash-cam footage which
OL,18,Fcould assist, to contact us on 101,
OL,19,Fquoting reference number 1950 27/05/
OL,20,F26."
